node.text:
A few of the boys picked up the bags and Howies boards to see who could rack up the most points with 8 tosses! Who came out on top? Cheese of course! 🔥 if you voted for Cheese, watch out for our story, you could win too! Want to play bags with Howies boards too? Click the link in bio to get yours!
—
#StickWithTheBest

node.text:
The boys competed their hearts out, but there can one be on gold medal winner and he is…. 🥁 DUTS with a nearly perfect toss! If you guessed Duts would toss the quarter, make sure to keep an eye on our story, you might win with him 🔥 Stay tuned for next weeks game 😎
—
#HowiesHockeyTape #HowiesSummerGames

node.text: The boys over at @bauerhockey came out with their new Nexus ADV and they tasked us with finding the best way to tape it. As experts in the tape game, the Howies boys explored different ideas on how to tape the new stick. #StickWithTheBest #SpoilYourStick

node.text:
We took the @egdgoaltending boys on an exclusive behind-the-scenes look at our headquarters in Grand Rapids, Michigan! From our offices to our warehouse to our hangout space, we invite you to check out exactly where your hockey supplies are coming from and the people that make it happen every day. —
#StickWithTheBest #SpoilYourStick #EGDtv (🎥: @michaelkingfilms & @rickice92)
